Package: LearnTidyML
Title: Machine Learning Method Assistant
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Jason", "Geslois", email = "jason592470@duck.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive Shiny app to help users select appropriate ML methods
    based on their data characteristics. Provides data profiling, method recommendations,
    data cleaning, model training with comparison, and plain-English result explanations
    designed for educational use.
